text: Alice Bah Kuhnke (born Alice Bah 21 December 1971) is a Swedish politician and television presenter. In October 2014, she became the Minister of Culture and Democracy in Sweden under Stefan LÃ¶fven. She joined the Green Party three days before being appointed. Bah Kuhnke presented the Mickey Mouse Club during the early 1990s on SVT.
